  }, "v6"), mdx("p", null, "Sa-ra v\xE2ng ph\u1EE5c \xC1p-ra-ham, ch\u1ED3ng m\xECnh, g\u1ECDi \xF4ng l\xE0 ch\u1EE7 m\xECnh. Ch\u1ECB em s\u1EBD l\xE0 con ch\xE1u th\u1EADt c\u1EE7a Sa-ra n\u1EBFu ch\u1ECB em lu\xF4n lu\xF4n l\xE0m \u0111i\u1EC1u ph\u1EA3i, kh\xF4ng s\u1EE3 h\xE3i g\xEC. "), mdx("h6", {
